MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the DG9 postcode area of Stranraer.Our Engineers have managed to restore power to a number of properties in the area and we still expect all power to be restored by 7AM. We understand that to be without power is frustrating and we apologise for this. We will update this message if this information changes. Thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 3.09AM on 10th March 2021.
